    • Constructor Detail

      • LIBORVolatilityModelFromGivenMatrix

        public LIBORVolatilityModelFromGivenMatrix(TimeDiscretizationInterface timeDiscretization,
                                           TimeDiscretizationInterface liborPeriodDiscretization,
                                           double[][] volatility)
        Creates a simple volatility model using given piece-wise constant values on a given discretization grid.
        Parameters:
        timeDiscretization - Discretization of simulation time.
        liborPeriodDiscretization - Discretization of tenor times.
        volatility - Volatility matrix volatility[timeIndex][componentIndex] where timeIndex the index of the start time in timeDiscretization and componentIndex from liborPeriodDiscretization
